snippet.title: HI3 v4.2 [Rosemary's Nocturne] Trailer - Honkai Impact 3rd
snippet.description:
v4.2 [Rosemary's Nocturne] coming soon, S-rank Rita Rossweisse [Fallen Rosemary] debuts! A strange encounter leads to a more bizarre truth...
Story Chapter XIX [Into Earth does the Water Flow] released, Augment Core [Danzai Spectramancer] launched!
